-08-09T22:10:22+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-09T22:11:51+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-toolbox/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-toolbox/","content_html":""},{"title":"Posts","date_published":"2023-06-11T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-13T08:29:16+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/posts/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/posts/","content_html":""},{"title":"The Art Studio","date_published":"2023-05-31T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-09-09T21:00:37+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-art-studio/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-art-studio/","content_html":"\u003cp\u003eIf you\u0026rsquo;ve been enjoying my work and finding it entertaining. Your support means the world to me, and I can\u0026rsquo;t thank you enough for being a part of this journey.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you want to stay connected and show your support, you can follow or supported me on \u003ca href=\"https://ko-fi.com/errbufferoverfl\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eKo-Fi\u003c/a\u003e. It\u0026rsquo;s a fantastic way to help me create more amazing content and keep the creative juices flowing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"projects\"\u003eProjects\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"anarchic-illustrationsthe-art-studioanarchic-illustrationsmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-art-studio/anarchic-illustrations/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-art-studio/anarchic-illustrations/\"\u003eAnarchic Illustrations\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eDrawings, prints and stickers promoting the abolition of traditional forms of government and institutions.\nAll my anarchic themed illustrations are available as high-resolution downloads, available under CC by 4.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"digital-paintingsthe-art-studiodigital-paintingsmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-art-studio/digital-paintings/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-art-studio/digital-paintings/\"\u003eDigital Paintings\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eFeatures a wide-range of styles and themes that were created using digital tools and techniques. From digital-paintings to vector based art, you can find a variety of miscellaneous work here!\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"100-days-of-gouachethe-art-studioone-hundered-days-of-gouachemd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-art-studio/one-hundered-days-of-gouache/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-art-studio/one-hundered-days-of-gouache/\"\u003e100 Days of Gouache\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eThe concept of a 100 days project is you commit to doing something consistently for 100 days straight. For a non sequential 100 days I created a [[.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"linoprintsthe-art-studiolinoprintsmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-art-studio/linoprints/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-art-studio/linoprints/\"\u003eLinoprints\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"sketchesthe-art-studiosketchessketchesmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  \n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link broken\"\n  data-src=\"the-art-studio/sketches/sketches\"\u003eSketches\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eAll my sketches as I learn how to make better pictures, and communicate visually. See my progress as I improve my skills and learn new techniques in the art of sketches.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"work-in-progressthe-art-studiowork-in-progressmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-art-studio/work-in-progress/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-art-studio/work-in-progress/\"\u003eWork in Progress\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eSupporters Only\nFeatures a range of work in progress, including sketches, colour drafts and time-lapse videos. Take a sneak peek into the evolution of some of my creations as they develop from initial concepts to fully-fleshed out designs!\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"mediums\"\u003eMediums\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"gouachethe-notebookgouachemd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-notebook/gouache/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-notebook/gouache/\"\u003eGouache\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"woodblockthe-notebookwoodblockmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/the-notebook/woodblock/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/the-notebook/woodblock/\"\u003eWoodblock\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n"},{"title":"The Anti-Library","date_published":"2023-05-28T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-09-09T17:53:45+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-antilibrary/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-antilibrary/","content_html":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ea scholar conscious of the power of [their] antilibrary is not concerned with treating knowledge as a property to possess or consume; rather [\u0026hellip;] how much you don’t know—and how to find out that information when you need it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e- Giovanni da Col, HAU: Journal of Ethnographic Theory\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"before-you-begin\"\u003eBefore you begin…\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe notes and summaries included in these pages are snippets that remind me, or help me relate and explore high-level concepts. They aren\u0026rsquo;t a summary of the chapter or book! If you look through these notes and like the ideas, disagree with them, or you find yourself synthesising new ideas, I recommend you read the whole book!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"up-next\"\u003eUp Next\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"current\"\u003eCurrent\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"section-ul\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/how-to-stand-up-to-a-dictator.png\" alt=\"How to Stand Up to a Dictator Book Cover\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/how-to-stand-up-to-a-dictator/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/how-to-stand-up-to-a-dictator/\"\u003eHow to Stand Up to a Dictator\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eWhat will you sacrifice for the truth? Maria Ressa has spent decades speaking truth to power. But her work tracking disinformation networks seeded by her own government, spreading lies to its own citizens laced with anger and hate, has landed her in trouble with the most powerful man in the country: President Duterte.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"past\"\u003ePast\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"section-ul\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/power-hungry.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/power-hungry/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/power-hungry/\"\u003ePower Hungry\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eTwo unsung women whose power using food as a political weapon during the civil rights movement was so great it brought the ire of government agents working against them In early 1969 Cleo Silvers and a few Black Panther Party members met at a community center laden with boxes of donated food to cook for the neighborhood children.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/stasiland.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/stasiland/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/stasiland/\"\u003eStasiland\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eStasiland tells true stories of people who heroically resisted the communist dictatorship of East Germany, and of people who worked for its secret police, the Stasi.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/the-2020-commission-report-on-the-north-korean-nuclear-attacks-against-the-united-states.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/the-2020-commission-report-on-the-north-korean-nuclear-attacks-against-the-united-states/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/the-2020-commission-report-on-the-north-korean-nuclear-attacks-against-the-united-states/\"\u003eThe 2020 Commission Report on the North Korean Nuclear Attacks Against The United States\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003e\u0026lsquo;A book with a ferocious pace and more black humour than one could imagine\u0026rsquo;– Evening Standard As heard on BBC Radio 4 The World Tonight America lost 1.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/chasing-shadows.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/chasing-shadows/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/chasing-shadows/\"\u003eChasing Shadows\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eFrom Irish revolutionaries to the Christchurch massacre and the rise of right wing extremism, Chasing Shadows uncovers the long and brutal history of terrorism in Australia.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/why-you-should-give-a-f-ck-about-farming.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/why-you-should-give-a-f-ck-about-farming/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/why-you-should-give-a-f-ck-about-farming/\"\u003eWhy you should give a f*ck about farming\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eThere is no farmers and others. If you eat or wear clothes, the decisions you make influence farming. ‘Eaters will be the ultimate arbiter of where and how food is grown and how the land is cared for \u0026hellip; We all have a stake in the future of food and farming.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/ghost-work.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/ghost-work/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/ghost-work/\"\u003eGhost Work\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003e\u0026ldquo;A startling exposé of the invisible human workforce that powers the web\u0026ndash;and how to bring it out of the shadows. Hidden beneath the surface of the internet, a new, stark reality is looming\u0026ndash;one that cuts to the very heart of our endless debates about the impact of AI.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/the-feminist-and-the-sex-offender.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/the-feminist-and-the-sex-offender/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/the-feminist-and-the-sex-offender/\"\u003eThe Feminist and the Sex Offender\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eIn the era of Me Too and mass incarceration, The Feminist and the Sex Offender makes a powerful feminist case for accountability without punishment and sexual safety and pleasure without injustice.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/anarchic-agreements-a-field-guide-to-collective-organising.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/anarchic-agreements-a-field-guide-to-collective-organising/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/anarchic-agreements-a-field-guide-to-collective-organising/\"\u003eAnarchic Agreements, a Field Guide to Collective Organising\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eA new world is possible and not just in our hearts. Anarchic Agreements is a quintessential field guide for the revolution, answering the practical questions often left out of works of political theory and philosophy.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/lost-in-work-escaping-capitalism.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/lost-in-work-escaping-capitalism/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/lost-in-work-escaping-capitalism/\"\u003eLost in Work Escaping Capitalism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003e\u0026lsquo;Work hard, get paid.\u0026rsquo; It\u0026rsquo;s simple. Self-evident. But it\u0026rsquo;s also a lie—at least for most of us. For young people today, the old assumptions are crumbling; hard work in school no longer guarantees a secure, well-paying job in the future.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/revolution-at-point-zero.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/revolution-at-point-zero/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/revolution-at-point-zero/\"\u003eRevolution at Point Zero\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eWritten between 1974 and 2016, Revolution at Point Zero collects four decades of research and theorising on the nature of housework, social reproduction, and women’s struggles on this terrain—to escape it, to better its conditions, to reconstruct it in ways that provide an alternative to capitalist relations.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"incomplete\"\u003eIncomplete\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"section-ul\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/expect-resistance-a-crimethinc-field-manual.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/expect-resistance-a-crimethinc-field-manual/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/expect-resistance-a-crimethinc-field-manual/\"\u003eExpect Resistance: A Crimethink Field Manual\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eExpect Resistance is not one but three books, each of which may be read as a complete work unto itself. The first book, printed in standard black ink, continues the inquiry into modern life and its discontents begun in Days of War, Nights of Love.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/the-antilibrary/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/the-antilibrary/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism/\"\u003eThe Age of Surveillance Capitalism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eThe challenges to humanity posed by the digital future, the first detailed examination of the unprecedented form of power called \u0026lsquo;surveillance capitalism,\u0026rsquo; and the quest by powerful corporations to predict and control us.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n"},{"title":"The-soapboxes","date_published":"2021-09-13T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-15T22:12:17+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-soapbox/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-soapbox/","content_html":""}]}